bitfield.description: This bit allows to enable or disable the LP mode of the DPLL4. Writting this bit to switch the mode between LP or normal mode will take effect only when the DPLL will have transition into the bypass or stop state, followed by a lock or re-lock of the DPLL.

Enables the DPLL LP mode to enter the LP mode at the following lock or re-lock sequence.

bitfield.description: Write 0s for future compatibility. Read returns 0.
